This is a cursor rule to explicitly create a custom tab for a Salesforce object.

File Naming Convention: OBJECT_NAME.tab-meta.xml

Example:
New custom object: 'Test Object'

File name: Test_Object__c.tab-meta.xml

Custom tab xml
<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?>
<CustomTab xmlns="http://soap.sforce.com/2006/04/metadata">
    <customObject>true</customObject>
    <motif>Custom70: Handsaw</motif>
</CustomTab>


